<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">RiveLogger.levels </span><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">=</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;"> [.debug] </span><span style="--shiki-light:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#6A737D;">// 过滤日志级别；默认为所有级别</span></span>
